---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Return & Refund Policy - MSZ Software House">
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter">Return & Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-charcoal-800/80 dark:text-gray-300">
          Last updated: December 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              At MSZ Software House, we strive to provide high-quality digital products and services. Due to the nature of digital products, our refund policy is designed to be fair while protecting our intellectual property.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Digital Products Refund Policy</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Wrong Purchase:</strong> You purchased the WRONG product by mistake and have NOT downloaded or accessed it</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Issues:</strong> File/link is corrupted and cannot be replaced or fixed</li>
              <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> Digital product was not delivered within 24 hours of payment</li>
              <li><strong>Misrepresentation:</strong> Product significantly differs from description (must be reported within 24 hours)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">NOT Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Digital products already downloaded or accessed</li>
              <li>Templates, courses, or eBooks already viewed</li>
              <li>Change of mind after successful delivery</li>
              <li>Compatibility issues with your device/software (check requirements before purchase)</li>
              <li>User error or misunderstanding of product features</li>
              <li>Requests made after 48 hours of purchase</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Services Refund Policy</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> Service was not delivered and project didn't start within agreed timeline</li>
              <li><strong>Breach of Agreement:</strong> We failed to meet the agreed service specifications</li>
              <li><strong>Cancellation:</strong> Project cancelled before work begins (full refund)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Partial Refunds</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Project cancelled after work has begun (refund based on work completed)</li>
              <li>Milestone-based projects (refund for incomplete milestones only)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">NOT Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Completed services that meet agreed specifications</li>
              <li>Client-requested changes beyond original scope</li>
              <li>Services cancelled due to client non-cooperation</li>
              <li>Change of mind after project completion</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">SaaS Subscriptions Refund Policy</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> SaaS access was not delivered within 12 hours</li>
              <li><strong>Invalid Access:</strong> Provided credentials don't work and cannot be fixed</li>
              <li><strong>Service Discontinued:</strong> Original provider discontinues the service</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">NOT Eligible for Refund</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Successfully used SaaS access (even for 1 day)</li>
              <li>Account suspended due to user violation of provider's terms</li>
              <li>Provider policy changes (beyond our control)</li>
              <li>User sharing credentials leading to account suspension</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Refund Process</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How to Request a Refund</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Contact us within 48 hours of purchase via email: mszsoftwarehouse@gmail.com</li>
              <li>Provide your order number and payment receipt</li>
              <li>Clearly state the reason for refund request</li>
              <li>Provide any supporting evidence (screenshots, error messages, etc.)</li>
            </ol>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Processing Time</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Refund requests are reviewed within 24-48 hours</li>
              <li>Approved refunds are processed within 3-5 business days</li>
              <li>Refunds are issued through the original payment method</li>
              <li>Bank transfer refunds may take 5-7 business days to reflect</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Return Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Since we deal with digital products and services, traditional "returns" don't apply. However:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Digital Products:</strong> Cannot be "returned" once accessed, but eligible for refund under specific conditions</li>
              <li><strong>Services:</strong> Work-in-progress can be cancelled with partial refund based on completion</li>
              <li><strong>SaaS Access:</strong> Can be discontinued, but refunds only under eligible conditions</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Exceptions</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We reserve the right to make exceptions to this policy in cases of:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              <li>Technical errors on our part</li>
              <li>Exceptional circumstances beyond customer control</li>
              <li>Long-term customer relationships and goodwill</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              For refund requests or questions about this policy:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-charcoal-800 dark:text-gray-300">
              <li><strong>Email:</strong> mszsoftwarehouse@gmail.com</li>
              <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-cream-100 dark:bg-charcoal-800 rounded-lg border border-cream-400 dark:border-charcoal-700">
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-center">
              This policy is designed to be fair to both customers and MSZ Software House.<br>
              Last updated: December 2025 | Â© 2025 MSZ Software House. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>